{"Author":"Kalle Launiala","Body":"The Ball design is ultimately and foremost bent to serve information ownership. It does not equal to copyrights or monetizing the information, while it does provide the infrastructure to achieve that as well.\u000a\u000aThe better analogue is following: if you can access and copy something, you can do the same thing with The Ball as well. It's a digital open accelerator for any information management. The public cloud running intances provide durability, the home-device-running ones provide absolute privacy.","Categories":{"CollectionContent":[{"CategoryName":"catSolutions","Excerpt":"The end user\/customer\/citizen approaching value-adding solutions","ID":"95c40a72-4430-4e25-8bfb-d1c62a81521e","ImageData":{"AdditionalFormatFileExt":".jpg","ContentLength":348837,"FileExt":".jpg","ID":"e9cc5c8b-2ba2-4521-a2d3-972b78ab1e56","MasterETag":null,"Name":"MediaContent","OriginalFileName":null,"OwnerID":"00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000","RelativeLocation":"grp\/90eb1c69-169c-491c-a75f-ce883b840a9b\/AaltoGlobalImpact.OIP\/MediaContent\/e9cc5c8b-2ba2-4521-a2d3-972b78ab1e56.jpg","SemanticDomainName":"AaltoGlobalImpact.OIP"},"MasterETag":null,"Name":"Category","OwnerID":"00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000","ParentCategory":null,"ParentCategoryID":"69f65952-b4b0-46a2-bbf3-c3b8d639e445","ReferenceToInformation":null,"RelativeLocation":"grp\/90eb1c69-169c-491c-a75f-ce883b840a9b\/AaltoGlobalImpact.OIP\/Category\/95c40a72-4430-4e25-8bfb-d1c62a81521e","SemanticDomainName":"AaltoGlobalImpact.OIP","Title":"Solutions"},{"CategoryName":"catAboutTheBall","Excerpt":"About \"The Ball\" - whatever it might relate to...","ID":"e400ecb5-650c-4837-a18f-a5b77c8722fd","ImageData":{"AdditionalFormatFileExt":".jpg","ContentLength":53763,"FileExt":".jpg","ID":"cacfab91-76cc-4a02-ab6a-7b835e8bc0fc","MasterETag":null,"Name":"MediaContent","OriginalFileName":null,"OwnerID":"00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000","RelativeLocation":"grp\/90eb1c69-169c-491c-a75f-ce